            "body": "added some other smaller `build zig` improvements:\r\n\r\n- `zig build functionaltest` and similar now handles Ctrl-C properly\r\n\r\n- cross-compilation often do not need to be explicitly requested, see news.txt blurb\r\n\r\n- `zig fmt --check` is run in CI.",
